// @tags: stdlib, sys, intrinsics, comparison, ordering
// @description: Comprehensive tests for comparison intrinsics that provide
//               type-safe comparisons for various types.
//
// Coverage:
// - Equality: eq, ne
// - Ordering: lt, le, gt, ge
// - Type coverage: integers, floats, bools, chars, pointers
// - Special cases: NaN comparisons, pointer comparisons
